org.interledger.codecs.packettypes

インタフェース InterledgerPacketType

  • 既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    InterledgerErrorPacketType, InterledgerPacketType.AbstractInterledgerPacketType, PaymentPacketType, QuoteByDestinationAmountRequestPacketType, QuoteByDestinationAmountResponsePacketType, QuoteBySourceAmountRequestPacketType, QuoteBySourceAmountResponsePacketType, QuoteLiquidityRequestPacketType, QuoteLiquidityResponsePacketType

    public interface InterledgerPacketType
    An interface that defines how Interledger Packets are typed using ASN.1 OER encoding.

    • メソッドの詳細

      • fromTypeId

        static InterledgerPacketType fromTypeId(int type)
                                 throws InterledgerPacketType.InvalidPacketTypeException
        A helper method that will translate an integer into an instance of InterledgerPacketType. Note that this method only handled standard Interledger packets types. To operate upon non-standard packets, a different method should be used.
        パラメータ:
        type - The integer type.
        戻り値:
        An instance of InterledgerPacketType.
        例外:
        InterledgerPacketType.InvalidPacketTypeException - If the supplied type is invalid.

      • getTypeIdentifier

        Integer getTypeIdentifier()
        The packet's type identifier, as specified by IL-RFC-3.
        戻り値:
        An Integer representing the type of this packet.

      • getTypeUri

        URI getTypeUri()
        A URI representing the formal type of this packet per the Interledger Header Type registry maintained at IANA.
        戻り値:
        An instance of String.
        関連項目:
        "http://www.iana.org/assignments/interledger-header-types"
